data.description:
Embrace elegance on a sprawling almost 10-acre estate featuring a 3500 sq ft with a timeless design. The grand foyer leads to open living spaces, a chef-style kitchen, and a ground-floor primary bedroom sanctuary. Enjoy outdoor paradise with patios, an outdoor kitchen, and landscaped gardens.  The negotiable price allows you to transform this residence into your dream home. Perfect for a private estate, bed and breakfast, or development, explore the luxury, customization, and value in this unique estate!

The chef-style kitchen, complete with an expansive dining area, seamlessly connects to a family room, setting the stage for entertaining and creating enduring memories. The backyard oasis, featuring open and covered patios, an outdoor kitchen, and meticulously landscaped gardens, is a true paradise. While this residence boasts a captivating floorplan, abundant natural light, and built-in shelving, it's important to note that it offers a unique opportunity for customization. 

Priced to sell, this exceptional property is open to negotiation, offering the discerning buyer the chance to further customize and transform it into their dream home.  Embrace the perfect blend of luxury, customization, and negotiability in this extraordinary property! 

All information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. It is the sole responsibility of the buyer and buyer's agent to verify all information. Property will be sold "AS-IS". Sellers replacing roof and will make no additional repairs. "Subject to" offers will not be accepted.
